s, that he continued until his death. He made use the Copernican\nsystem for his calculations, comparing them occasionally with calculations\nusing new Ptolemaic based ephemerides and in his last almanacs with\ncalculations based on Tycho Brahes' model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Dec 2017 17:00:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-03"}
