larity barycenters have\nmoved around, the AR produced flares without CME. If these properties found for\nthe movement of the barycenters are generic pre-cursors of CME eruption (or\nlack of it), identifying them may serve as an excellent pre-condition for\nrefining the forecast of the lift-off of CMEs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 31 Dec 2017 13:18:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-24"}
